title: Fischer-Z - Highlights 1979 - 2004
description: John Watts (the heart & soul of Fischer Z) is one of the UKs most under-rated song writers. Strangely enough they were supported in Europe by The Police early in both their careers. The Police took off but Fischer Z didn&#039;t (at least in the UK - in Europe they have a lot more fans). This double CD &#039;best of&#039; show cases the bands best tracks which vary from rock to reggae and more inbetween. From love songs (So Long) to protest songs - it&#039;s all in there.
